column2: SELECT INTO MyDB.photo_lim L.grpid, SPO.specObjID, SPO.ra, SPO.dec, SPO.z, SPO.modelMag_u, SPO.modelMag_g, SPO.modelMag_r, SPO.modelMag_i, SPO.modelMag_z FROM MyDB.Lim as L OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbySpecObjEq (L.ra, L.dec, L.aperture) as SO INNER JOIN SpecPhotoAll as SPO on SPO.SpecObjID = SO.SpecObjID WHERE SPO.class = # and abs (SPO.z - L.zcmb) < # * sqrt (#) * L.sigma
